ygData.subject: Re: Banks
ygData.msgSnippet: Getting twinked is part of the game. I think if someone has another character that has the skill to make cool stuff, or the level to hunt and get awsome stuff,
ygData.messageBody:
Getting twinked is part of the game. I think if someone has another character
that has the skill to make cool stuff, or the level to hunt and get awsome
stuff, they should be allowed to do what they want with it. So getting
twinked is part of the game, and it happens. Heck, the other day, one of the
few Level 50 characters, made a new character, had him going with level 49
armor, and really high level weapons and stuff. Looked awsome, he made level
8 in an hour. Guess it is just part of the game.

Kondor, Half Elf Paladin
~Veeshan~
